import React from 'react'
import { Col, Container, Row } from 'react-bootstrap'

const Section = () => {
  return (
    <section>
      <Container>
      <Row>
      <Col><Row></Row>
      <Row></Row>
      </Col>
      <Col></Col>
      <Col></Col>
      <Col></Col>
      </Row>
      </Container>
    </section>
  )
}

export default Section
